            <title>[INT-1144] Add JsonMesssageConvertor support in jSI JMS</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/INT-1144</link>
                <project id="10121" key="INT">Spring Integration</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Noticed on the Spring Extensions se-amqp prototype there is a JsonMessageConvertor that uses Jackson. I think this would be useful in the integration jms package. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Are there any plans to add support for this? I&apos;ve seen the JSON Input/Outpout Mappers and the ticket for the JSON Transformer.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks &lt;/p&gt;</description>
